  "texts": [
    "The Escape Room Challenge task tests agents on their ability to execute tasks both sequentially and in parallel, requiring the reasoning of temporal dependencies and the ability to synchronize actions.",
    "Second, we introduce a Directed Acyclic Graph Multi-Agent framework (VillagerAgent) to tackle complex dependencies in multi-agent collaborations.",
    "Each subtask is represented as a graph node in the DAG.",
    "We dynamically adjust the graph structure and the agent roles according to the environment and the agent states.",
    "VillagerAgent consists of task decomposer, agent controller, state manager and base agents."
  ],
